Lab 02 - Basic Routing 
objective
The objective of this lab was to simulate a real office 
network environment which included 2 departments — 
Network Operations and Finance. These departments are 
separated by a router between them.

This setup simulates what is logically done in companies 
where departments are separated for security purposes, 
but still need to communicate with each other through 
a controlled path — the router.

The success of the lab was confirmed after PC1 on 
Network 1 successfully pinged PC3 on Network 2.

